792
00:49:24,312 --> 00:49:26,228
<i>I came to show you some fabric.</i>

793
00:49:26,812 --> 00:49:28,437
<i>No, I don't need any.</i>

794
00:49:30,145 --> 00:49:31,394
<i>I told you!</i>

795
00:49:31,395 --> 00:49:32,728
<i>I don't need it!</i>

796
00:50:13,437 --> 00:50:14,937
