850
00:53:41,812 --> 00:53:43,895
I'm not complaining.

851
00:53:44,437 --> 00:53:46,311
<i>We are the ones who made Qingdao big.</i>

852
00:53:46,312 --> 00:53:50,228
<i>But we get paid like shit!</i>

853
00:53:53,853 --> 00:53:56,270
