here and get in single file.

857
00:54:18,353 --> 00:54:18,978
Okay.

858
00:54:18,978 --> 00:54:19,978
Help them.

859
00:54:20,020 --> 00:54:21,187
Hello.

860
00:54:21,978 --> 00:54:23,145
Give it here.

861
00:54:23,812 --> 00:54:26,852
