863
00:54:31,853 --> 00:54:33,227
No, it's close by.

864
00:54:33,228 --> 00:54:34,187
I see.

865
00:54:34,188 --> 00:54:35,769
Can you tell me the address?

866
00:54:35,770 --> 00:54:37,436
