877
00:55:18,645 --> 00:55:20,812
<i>Passport</i>
Should I put them in the safe?

878
00:55:21,520 --> 00:55:23,270
I can do that for you.

879
00:55:23,312 --> 00:55:24,561
Don't worry, I got it.

880
00:55:24,562 --> 00:55:26,353
