890
00:57:02,520 --> 00:57:03,977
<i>Send fax</i>

891
00:57:03,978 --> 00:57:05,437
<i>Subject: Call center pics</i>

892
00:57:13,187 --> 00:57:14,811
<i>Send fax</i>

893
00:57:14,812 --> 00:57:16,645
