1611
01:45:52,145 --> 01:45:54,478
Damn, look at you.

1612
01:45:54,687 --> 01:45:56,020
Can you even get up?

1613
01:45:59,020 --> 01:46:00,770
Do I still have my nose?

1614
01:46:00,812 --> 01:46:01,812
It's still there.

1615
01:46:02,103 --> 01:46:03,728
Duk-hee!

1616
01:46:08,978 --> 01:46:10,062
Are you all right?

1617
01:46:10,353 --> 01:46:12,353
